{
  "id": "adv_bond_kan_01_01",
  "title": "kana1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。坂本プロデューサーじゃないですか～\nこんなところで会えるなんて嬉しいです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your effort. Isn't that Producer Sakamoto~\nI'm so glad to meet you here~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.3870747884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaはですね〜、さっきまでそこのスタジオで\nレギュラー番組の収録をやってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana~‚ was just recording\na regular program in that studio",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3870747884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、kana達の番組、観てくれてたんですね\nありがとうございま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you watched kana's show\nThank you very mu~ch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8277321498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6340133667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ？　こいつ、前はもっと偉そうで）\n（人の弱み握ったら一生脅して回りそうな奴だったのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Huh? This guy used to be much more arrogant）\n（and seemed like he spent his whole life looking for other people's weak points and threatening them）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6340133667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "（な～んか、妙に腰が引けてるなぁ）\n（とうとう訴訟でも食らったかな～？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Some~thing‚ looks strangely hesitant）\n（I guess he ended up getting sued~?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1009969712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.093400383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "……え、mihoちゃんは元気……？\nはい、いつも通り元気にしてますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh‚ how is miho-chan…?\nYes‚ she's fine as always!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.093400383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "今日はkanaだけVTRの収録だったんですよ\n明後日はfranとmihoも一緒に来ますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ only kana was recording a VTR\nfran and miho will come tomorrow‚ too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5829240481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3743754387
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "（あー、思い出した。mihoが前に）\n（ こいつからキモいメールが来たって愚痴ってたっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah‚ I remembered. miho had complained before）\n（about receiving unpleasant email from this guy）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3743754387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "（あの件、結局どうなったんだっけなぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder what happened to that incident in the end…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9069154422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8949427128
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、うちのマネージャーと三枝社長にも\n坂本さんに会ったって伝えておきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I'll tell my manager and President Saegusa\nthat I met Sakamoto-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8949427128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3752602737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "（お、顔色が変わった。……あぁ、そっか。三枝社長が）\n（裏から手を回して、こいつのこと黙らせたんだっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh‚ his face has changed color. …Ah‚ I see. President Saegusa）\n（pulled strings behind the scenes to silence this guy）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3752602737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "（今更だけど、三枝社長って何者なんだろ……）\n（……ま、今はそれはそれとして）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Now that I think about it‚ what is President Saegusa's identity…）\n（…Well‚ let's put that aside for now）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9144444943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7311338266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "坂本さん、今はなんの番組を担当されてるんですか？\nああ、あのお昼の帯番組！？　すご～い！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakamoto-san‚ what program are you in charge of now?\nAhh‚ that daytime show?! Amazing!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7311338266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.8792067052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "（今あの番組に出てて、こいつが声掛けそうな）\n（相手って言ったら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If there was someone on this show right now）\n（that this guy could talk to…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8792067052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.0854647797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、この間『恋々Poison』の麗亜ちゃんから\nちょっと困ったことがあるって相談があったんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ a while ago‚ I consulted with Rea from \"KoiKoi Poison\"\nabout something a little bit difficult~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0854647797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "今度お茶して聞いてこようかなって思ってるんですけど\nなんなんですかね～、kana心配で～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking of listening o it while drinking tea this time‚\nbut what could it be~‚ kana worried about her~……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5277321976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.7889338654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "（ビンゴ。懲りねえな、このプロデューサー）\n（ ま、それならそれで好都合だけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Bingo! This producer never learns）\n（Well‚ that would be a good thing）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7889338654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.0768018565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "え？　kanaが番組にゲスト出演？\nいいんですか～！？　さすが敏腕プロデューサー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? kana is a guest on a show?\nIs that okay~!? What a talented producer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0768018565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "その代わり、大事にはしないでくれ……？\nよく分かんないですけど、ご連絡お待ちしてます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In return‚ please don't cause any trouble…?\nI don't quite understand‚ but I'll wait for your contact!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5977317653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（ま、こんなもんかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Well‚ that's about it）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.198275614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.198275614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "（相手の弱みを握ってるんなら、使わなきゃ損じゃん）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even if I know my opponent's weak point‚ I'm at a loss if I don't use it）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_01-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "（麗亜に連絡して、もっといろいろ聞いてやろっと）\n（対処方法教えてやれば、べらべら喋ってくれそうだし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'll contact Rea and ask her more）\n（If I tell them how to cope‚ she'll probably talk a lot）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3280487857,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}